cs.MA, cs.AI, cs.CR, cs.DC, cs.SE 

This paper deals with the integration of multi-agent systems and smart contracts, which falls under the category of multi-agent systems (cs.MA) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also discusses the possibility of malicious agents disrupting the protocol, which relates to computer security and cryptography (cs.CR). The use of smart contracts also involves distributed computing (cs.DC) and software engineering (cs.SE).
